      <hedline>
        <hl1>Honey, We Forgot to Raise the Kids!</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>''Kids Gone Wild'' is pretty much on target. A better way to sum it up, though, is that well-adjusted emotionally secure parents provide clear boundaries and sound guidance that result in kids' being seen and heard for all the right reasons.</p>
        <p>Andrew Rothschild  Atlanta, Nov. 27, 2005</p>
      </block>
